%% Diagram: OAuth 2.1 flow selection decision tree
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TD
    Start{Who is acting?}
    Start -->|End user present| HasUI{Can the device<br/>render a browser?}
    Start -->|No user — service to service| CC[Client Credentials<br/>RFC 6749 section 4.4]

    HasUI -->|Yes — browser, mobile,<br/>desktop, SPA| AC[Authorization Code<br/>+ PKCE<br/>RFC 6749 section 4.1 plus RFC 7636]
    HasUI -->|No / input-constrained<br/>TV, CLI, IoT| DC[Device Authorization Grant<br/>RFC 8628]

    AC --> Refresh{Need long-lived<br/>session?}
    DC --> Refresh
    Refresh -->|Yes| RT[Refresh Token + rotation<br/>or sender-constraint<br/>OAuth 2.1]
    Refresh -->|No| Done([Issue access token only])

    AC -. Identity needed .-> OIDC[Add openid scope —<br/>OIDC Core 1.0 ID Token]
    DC -. Identity needed .-> OIDC

    Implicit[Implicit grant]
    ROPC[Resource Owner Password]
    Implicit -.->|Removed in OAuth 2_1| AC
    ROPC -.->|Removed in OAuth 2_1| AC

    classDef removed stroke:#c33,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 4 2
    class Implicit,ROPC removed
